'''淨化程式'''，也被稱為排毒程式，是一個有爭議的排毒計劃，由[[山達基|山達基]]教的創始人 [[羅恩·賀伯特|羅恩·賀伯特]]制定，在山達基教會被做為一個常態性的服務。<ref name="bouma">{{cite book|title=Australian Soul: Religion and Spirituality in the 21st Century |url=https://archive.org/details/australiansoulre00boum |first=Gary D. |last=Bouma|publisher=Cambridge University Press| year=2006|page=[https://archive.org/details/australiansoulre00boum/page/9 9]|isbn=0521673895}}</ref><ref name="refslund">{{cite book|last=Christensen|first=Dorthe Refslund|title=Scientology|url=https://archive.org/details/scientology00lewi|editor=James R. Lewis|publisher=Oxford University Press US|location=New York|year=2009|pages=[https://archive.org/details/scientology00lewi/page/n434 420]–421|chapter=Sources for the Study of Scientology|isbn=9780195331493}}</ref> 山達基認為，若要處理長期濫用藥物或暴露在有毒物質下的影響，淨化程式是唯一有效的方式。<ref name="refslund" /> 它形成戒毒康復和排毒程式的基礎，用於教會經營的屬下組織，如[[那可拿|那可拿]]、[[可明納|可明納]]、第二次機會<ref name="abq_denied">{{cite news|last=Proctor|first=Jeff|url=http://www.abqjournal.com/news/state/25104016state01-25-09.htm|title=Scientology Base Denied By Officials|date=January 25, 2009|work=Albuquerque Journal|accessdate=2009-02-14|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226010530/https://www.abqjournal.com/news/state/25104016state01-25-09.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 和國際戒毒專家學院。<ref name="nyp_rundown">{{cite news | first = John | last = DeSio | title = The Rundown on Scientology's Purification Rundown | url = http://www.nypress.com/article-16488-the-rundown-on-scientologys-purification-rundown.html | work = [[New_York_Press|New York Press]] | date = June 6, 2007 | accessdate = 2009-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090114163312/http://www.nypress.com/article-16488-the-rundown-on-scientologys-purification-rundown.html | archive-date = 2009-01-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 該程式包含運動、口服補品和久待蒸氣室（可能長達五小時，每週五天）。<ref name="nyp_rundown">{{cite news | first = John | last = DeSio | title = The Rundown on Scientology's Purification Rundown | url = http://www.nypress.com/article-16488-the-rundown-on-scientologys-purification-rundown.html | work = [[New_York_Press|New York Press]] | date = June 6, 2007 | accessdate = 2009-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090114163312/http://www.nypress.com/article-16488-the-rundown-on-scientologys-purification-rundown.html | archive-date = 2009-01-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 淨化程式的推廣，是看環境而不同的，是宗教的，也可是世俗的，是醫學的，也可是純粹精神上的。<ref name="welkos">{{cite news | last =Sappell | first =Joel | coauthors =Robert W. Welkos | work =[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | title =Church Seeks Influence in Schools, Business, Science | date =June 27, 1990 | url =http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-scientology062790,0,2470065,full.story | accessdate =2009-01-21 | archive-date =2012-10-26 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20121026084227/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-scientology062790,0,2470065,full.story | dead-url =yes }}</ref><ref name="sommer3">{{cite news|title=Helping Spread the Word|last=Sommer|first=Mark|date=February 1, 2005|work=The Buffalo News}}</ref>

儘管教會舉出很多推薦人的支持，該程式已被許多醫生批評，因為效果未經證實，還有潛在的危險。<ref>{{cite web | first = Janet | last = Reitman | title = Inside Scientology | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/politics/story/9363363/inside_scientology/print | work = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | date = February 2, 2006 | accessdate = 2009-01-20 | archive-date = 2008-06-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080622123603/http://www.rollingstone.com/politics/story/9363363/inside_scientology/print | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="snr">{{cite news|last=Gianni|first=Luke|url=http://www.newsreview.com/sacramento/Content?oid=283982|title=Scientology does detox, David E. Root, M.D|accessdate=2009-01-20|date=February 22, 2007|work=[[Sacramento_News_&_Review|Sacramento News & Review]]|archive-date=2011-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110130095718/http://www.newsreview.com/sacramento/content?oid=283982|dead-url=no}}</ref> 就連山達基自己的報告也指出一些常見的副作用，如脫水、電解質紊亂（包括低血鈉和低血鉀）、熱相關疾病（如體溫過高）。<ref name="emergency1997">{{cite journal| last=Al-Zaki |first=Taleb|coauthor=B Tilman Jolly| title=Severe Hyponatremia After Purification |journal=Annals of Emergency Medicine |publisher=Mosby, Inc.|doi=10.1016/S0196-0644(97)70335-4 |volume=29 |issue=1 | pages=194–195| pmid=8998113|date=January 1997}}</ref> 該程式使用的大劑量維生素 B3（菸鹼酸）和高溫蒸氣，均超出安全水平。<ref name="nyp_rundown" /><ref name="ssnatch">{{cite book |author=Abgrall, Jean-Marie |title=Soul snatchers: The Mechanics of Cults |publisher=Algora Pub |location=New York |year=1999 |pages=219 |isbn=1-892941-04-X}}</ref> 然而教會鼓勵參與者表明副作用並以此為據聲稱毒素已被排出。<ref name="rtp">{{cite journal|last=Staudenmayer|first=Herman|year=1996|title=Clinical Consequences of the EI/MCS "Diagnosis": Two Paths |journal=Regulatory Toxicology and Pharmacology|publisher=Academic Press|volume=24|issue=1|pages=S96–S110|issn=0273-2300|doi=10.1006/rtph.1996.0084|pmid=8921563 }}</ref> 在醫學上，藥片和高溫的結合已被描述為具有可致命的潛力。<ref>{{cite news|title=The Prisoners of Saint Hill|last=Kelsey|first=Tim|coauthors=Mike Ricks|date=January 31, 1994|work=The Independent|page=(II) 1|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/the-prisoners-of-saint-hill-the-scientologists-call-it-babywatching-but-it-has-nothing-to-do-with-looking-after-infants-tim-kelsey-and-mike-ricks-investigate-the-potentially-dangerous-and-possibly-illegal-secret-treatment-that-the-worlds-largest-cult-uses-to-deal-with-difficult-members-1403815.html|accessdate=2009-02-17|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925054633/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/the-prisoners-of-saint-hill-the-scientologists-call-it-babywatching-but-it-has-nothing-to-do-with-looking-after-infants-tim-kelsey-and-mike-ricks-investigate-the-potentially-dangerous-and-possibly-illegal-secret-treatment-that-the-worlds-largest-cult-uses-to-deal-with-difficult-members-1403815.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>有些家庭起訴山達基教會，聲稱淨化程式使親屬死亡。<ref name="sptimes">{{cite web | first = Geoff | last = Dougherty | title = Store selling Scientology vitamin regimen raises concerns | url = http://www.sptimes.com/News/32899/Pasco/Store_selling_Sciento.html | work = [[St._Petersburg_Times|St. Petersburg Times]] | date = March 28, 1999 | accessdate = 2009-02-14 | archive-date = 2016-10-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161026164545/http://www.sptimes.com/News/32899/Pasco/Store_selling_Sciento.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 背景 ==
賀伯特提出他對菸酸的思想，在一本名為《全部有關輻射》的書。他聲稱，發現大劑量的維生素能減輕和防止輻射病。<ref name="atack142">{{cite book |first=Jon | last=Atack | year=1990| title = A Piece of Blue Sky: Scientology, Dianetics and L. Ron Hubbard Exposed |url=https://archive.org/details/pieceblueskyscie00atac |publisher = Lyle Stuart / Carol Publishing Group |isbn=0-8184-0499-X|page=[https://archive.org/details/pieceblueskyscie00atac/page/n49 142]}}</ref> 他以片劑形式銷售該抗輻射混合物，稱這是“[[黛安娜䫈|黛安娜䫈]]”。 於1958年，[[美國食品和藥物管理局|美國食品和藥物管理局]]收繳和銷毀了21,000片,因為輻射治療的標籤誤導。<ref>{{cite book|last=Williams|first=Ian|title=The Alms Trade: Charities, Past, Present and Future|publisher=Cosimo|year=2007|pages=130|isbn=1602067538}}</ref>

1979年，淨化程式的前身被稱為“汗水計劃”，並同樣旨在消除迷幻藥的痕跡，據賀伯特，它仍然長期留在體內。<ref name="refslund" /><ref name="atack254">{{cite book |first=Jon | last=Atack | year=1990| title = A Piece of Blue Sky: Scientology, Dianetics and L. Ron Hubbard Exposed |publisher = Lyle Stuart / Carol Publishing Group |isbn=0-8184-0499-X|page=254}}</ref> 參加者飲食受限制，包括吃大劑量的維生素和一茶匙的鹽，每天至少花了一個小時，穿橡膠衣慢跑。對某一些人，這個方案持續好幾個月。<ref name="atack254" />

淨化程式是發展給[[那可拿|那可拿]]中心使用的，並發表在賀伯特的《戴尼提和山達基技術公告》以及《清除身體，清醒頭腦》一書。
<ref name="refslund"/><ref name="nyp_rundown" /> 另外兩本書描述這程式，《淨化：毒品答案圖解》和《那可拿新生活排毒計劃：羅恩·賀伯特有效的淨化程式》。術語“淨化程式“是一個“宗教技術中心”（治理[[山達基|山達基]]教會的機構）的[[商標|商標]]。雖然宗教技術中心的發言人否認有任何發牌給那可拿的安排。<ref name="bostonherald1998" />

== 程式 ==
該程序通常需要二～三個星期。除了花時間在烤箱，人們需要做運動，包括[[健美操|健美操]]，跑步機，以及其他類似的活動。<ref name="emergency1997" />

該方案包括定期劑量的維生素（尤其是[[菸鹼酸|菸鹼酸]]），長期在[[桑拿|桑拿]]中，運動，混合植物油，他們相信毒素會隨汗而出，植物油更換在體內的脂肪組織。<ref name="mccall">{{cite journal|last=McCall|first=W. Vaughn|year=2007|title=Psychiatry and Psychology in the Writings of L. Ron Hubbard |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-religion-and-health_2007-09_46_3/page/437|journal=Journal of Religion and Health|publisher=Springer Netherlands|volume=46|issue=3|pages=437–447|issn=1573-6571|doi=10.1007/s10943-006-9079-9}}</ref> 《清新身體，清新心靈》建議，整個過程中參加者維持正常飲食，以新鮮蔬菜補充。<ref name="cbcm19" />

淨化程式要求參與者定期攝取以下的：

* 多維生素雞尾酒，其中主要成分是[[菸酸|菸酸]]。《清除身體，清醒頭腦》建議開始劑量為100毫克，增加至5000毫克。<ref name="nyp_rundown" /> 對比之下，醫生建議的水平約15毫克：大劑量可產生嚴重的，甚至可能致命的副作用。<ref name="nyp_rundown" /> 參加者被告知要期待有中毒症狀，由於毒素或輻射從他們的身體脂肪釋放。<ref name="rtp">{{cite journal|last=Staudenmayer|first=Herman|year=1996|title=Clinical Consequences of the EI/MCS "Diagnosis": Two Paths |journal=Regulatory Toxicology and Pharmacology|publisher=Academic Press|volume=24|issue=1|pages=S96–S110|issn=0273-2300|doi=10.1006/rtph.1996.0084|pmid=8921563 }}</ref> 因此，菸鹼酸過量的影響，其中包括皮膚紅腫，潮紅（生理學），頭暈和頭痛，被解釋為對程式的積極作用。<ref name="nyp_rundown" /><ref name="rtp" /><ref name="ebner1996" />
* 礦物質補充劑，包括[[鈣|鈣]]，[[鎂|鎂]]，[[鐵|鐵]]，[[鋅|鋅]]，[[錳|錳]]，[[銅|銅]]，[[碘|碘]]和[[鉀|鉀]]。<ref>{{cite book|last=Hubbard|first=L. Ron|title=Clear Body, Clear Mind|publisher=New Era Publications International|location=Copenhagen|year=2002|pages=86–94|isbn=9788779686236}}</ref>
* 每天半杯純油，以取代那些在桑拿浴隨汗而出的油。<ref name="mccall" />
* “Cal-Mag”，一種飲品，《清除身體，清醒頭腦》描述為一個葡萄糖酸鈣，碳酸鎂和[[醋|醋]]的溶液，在組合比例上元素[[鈣|鈣]]為[[鎂|鎂]]的兩倍多。<ref>{{cite book|last=Hubbard|first=L. Ron|title=Clear Body, Clear Mind|publisher=New Era Publications International|location=Copenhagen|year=2002|pages=63–65|isbn=9788779686236}}</ref> 這是每天飲三次。<ref name="mccall" />
* 足夠的液體來取代在桑拿浴失去的。<ref name="cbcm19">{{cite book|last=Hubbard|first=L. Ron|title=Clear Body, Clear Mind|publisher=New Era Publications International|location=Copenhagen|year=2002|page=19|isbn=9788779686236}}</ref>

賀伯特規定，每個參與者每天必須完成報告，列出維生素，礦物質，Cal-Mag和其它流體的數額，經過檢討，以確保它們全面符合計劃。<ref name="cbcm113">{{cite book|last=Hubbard|first=L. Ron|title=Clear Body, Clear Mind|publisher=New Era Publications International|location=Copenhagen|year=2002|pages=113–115|isbn=9788779686236}}</ref>

淨化程式費用，在1990年大概是二千美元。<ref name="welkos">{{cite news | last =Sappell | first =Joel | coauthors =Robert W. Welkos|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | title=Church Seeks Influence in Schools, Business, Science | date =June 27, 1990|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-scientology062790,0,2470065,full.story |accessdate=2009-01-21}}</ref> 在1996年有折扣下是$1,790<ref name="ebner1996">{{cite news|last=Ebner|first=Mark|title=Do You Want To Buy A Bridge?|work=[[Spy_magazine|Spy magazine]]|url=http://www.hollywoodinterrupted.com/archives/ebner_undercover_scientology_spy_magazine_1996.phtml|accessdate=2009-01-27|date=February 1996|archive-date=2017-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170721035209/http://www.hollywoodinterrupted.com/archives/ebner_undercover_scientology_spy_magazine_1996.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> （雖然在1996年，另一個來源聲稱，四個星期的課程是四千美元左右），<ref name="rtp" /> 在1998年是$1,200<ref name="bostonherald1998">{{cite news|work=[[Boston_Herald|Boston Herald]] | last=Mallia|first=Joseph| date=March 3, 1998| title=Scientology reaches into schools through Narconon}}</ref> $5,200在2009年。<ref name="slt_quietly">{{cite news|url=http://www.sltrib.com/news/ci_12078368|title=More state funds quietly budgeted to help cops sweat to health|last=Carlisle|first=Nate|coauthors=Robert Gehrke|date=April 5, 2009|work=The Salt Lake Tribune|accessdate=2009-04-06|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308023718/https://www.sltrib.com/news/ci_12078368/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《清除身體，清醒頭腦》包含一個聲明，指出淨化程式不是一種醫療。<ref name="nyp_rundown" /> 類似的聲明出現在《賀伯特通訊辦公室公告》，指出淨化程式不是醫療過程，而是一個純粹精神活動。<ref name="nyp_rundown" /> 賀伯特建議，參加者須簽署一份棄權，指出淨化不是醫療。<ref name="nyp_rundown" />

